  <brief_title>Heart Rate Variability &amp; Fatty Acid Status: Haemodialysis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Heart Rate Variability and Omega-3 Fatty Acid Status in Haemodialysis Patients: an Observational Pilot Study</official_title>
